txt.en: You have turned in a stack of trophies for a modest reward suitable for a collector such as yourself.
Wanted: Armoured carapaces from the insects near Gath Forthnír. Deilvery of the items should be made to Areneth at the hidden Ranger-outpost.
'We will find a use for this.'
'The carapaces of the insects around are sturdy. We can find many uses for them here.'
Council of the North Task: Armoured Carapaces
The Rangers at Gath Forthnír await a delivery of armoured carapaces to be made to Areneth.
Deliver the armoured carapaces to Areneth at Gath Forthnír in Angmar
You have accepted a task to collect and deliver armoured carapaces from the insects near Gath Forthnír to Areneth at the hidden Ranger-camp.
Wanted: Armoured carapaces from the insects near Gath Forthnír.
